browse_grid_objects.product_name: Abingdon Hall Tree 70cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
features_array: Overall: 175cm H x 70cm W x 32cm D

quickview_content.productComments: This is just fabulous. I don’t know why I didn’t buy one before. I am not good at flat packs but this was just so so easy. It took under a hour but to other people probably a lot less . Thanku Wayfair

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Hall Tree 100cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments:
Excellent value functional coat / shoe unit , quality better than expected.
Well packed self assembly kit with instructions however these need some careful study before 
assembly.  There are some misleading instructions especially regarding the top shelf (10) but with a bit of study its easy to figure out

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Jalynn Hall Tree 98cm Wide

quickview_content.productComments:
Easy to put together!
I had one piece broken, but got ne one delivered really quick! Easy to put together. Hooks are not attached in anyway so they keep moving, not a big problem for me I guess they could be attached with some small skrews or double sided tape if you want. Really pleased with the unit!

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Hat and Coat Hallway Unit
features_array: Overall: 180cm H x 72cm W x 33.7cm D

quickview_content.productComments: It was surprisingly straightforward to put together, it’s very sturdy and looks fantastic in our hallway. The shoe racks are tall / deep enough to fit my husband’s shoes comfortably which makes it look neater! Would highly recommend.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Abrum Hall Tree 80cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments: I recently purchased and I couldnt be happier with my decision! The quality of the materials is top-notch, and the craftsmanship is evident in every detail. Its both stylish and functional, fitting perfectly into my space and enhancing the overall look of my room.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Jenifer Hall Tree 80cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
features_array: Overall: 178.5cm H x 80cm W x 30cm D

quickview_content.productComments: Reminds me of my school days. For the price it was easy to assemble and looks fantastic. If you are like me and are looking for a good solution to coat and shoe storage that won’t cost the earth I highly recommend this and it fits my space requirements.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Alper Hall Tree 100cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
features_array: Overall: 184cm H x 100cm W x 40cm D

quickview_content.productComments: I wanted something that would look good enough to be on show in my living room as I dont have a hallway. This fits the bill perfectly and keeps me organised. It was really easy to assemble on my own with everything clearly labelled, even a screwdriver included, and step by step instructions. Feels very sturdy and looks a lot more expensive than it was, love it!

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Hall Tree 84cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
features_array: The hall tree bench comes with two anti-tip kits to secure it to the wall.
Aiming to satisfy various storage needs, the lower shelf can be assembled on either the left or right side.
Comes with detailed assembly instructions and numbered parts and hardware, the entryway hall rack wont take you long to set up.

quickview_content.productComments: I love this hall stand I brought it with the intention of making slight alterations. They sold one with a mirror but it was to wide so I bought this one and put a mirror on it

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Alemar Hall Tree 101.52cm Wide with Shoe Storage
Amista Hall Tree 85cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments: This is sturdy and looks great but needs securing properly to a wall - not ideal for completely free standing

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Allenton Hall Tree 70cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Absolutely love this & it fits perfectly in a small hallway. Easy to build too! Great look, price & value!

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Hall Tree 71.5cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
features_array: Overall: 182.5cm H x 71.5cm W x 34cm D

quickview_content.productComments: Sturdy, easy to make hall tree. Has made my corridor/hall look bigger and given it that special look. Good height (and takes up to 120kg) bench to sit on for people with mobility issues. Unlike some of the others on the website, this one does not go right back to the wall, but is a personal choice, and of course depends on your requirement. To me, it gives extra character to the stand.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Shoe Storage Hall Tree with Lakay
features_array: Condition: Brand new, modern hallway coat rack
Four open shelves for convenient storage
Constructed from 18 mm thick particleboard with melamine veneer finish
Equipped with four sturdy metal hooks for hanging

quickview_content.productComments: Packing and delivery was fine, building the unit was straight forward, however, the contents included an extra shoe section divider instead of one shelf. I have contacted them regarding this but I have received no reply.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Aliehs Hall Tree 30cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Fantastic product

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Hopewell Hall Tree with Bench and Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments:
Awesome coat rack! Very stylish and fairly easy to assemble even without prior experience in putting together flat packs. 

A word of advise, don’t bother with paper instructions, watch a video, makes much more sense!

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Luder Hall Tree 117cm Wide with Shoe Storage
features_array: Multi-use design: A coat rack with shoe storage, is suitable for family use. Comes with five hooks, five side shelves, and two long bottom shelves.
Steel frame, with adjustable feet: Hall tree has a strong core. Easy to keep the balance on uneven grounds.
Industrial-style coat and shoe rack: A striking dark colour, this brings a rustic feel into your space.
Anti-tipping straps: Attach this coat rack stand so it doesn't fall forward - safe for family homes.
Dimensions: 169H x 117W x 38Dcm. Maximum 50kg. Assembly required.

quickview_content.productComments: Nice product but The item number 10 does have a crack on it. Noticed straight away when i open the box.could you send a replacement?

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Atiim Hall Tree 80cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
Allensworth Hall Tree 72cm Wide with Shoe Storage
features_array: Perfect design: Perfect industrial style design, smooth lines. This coat stand is used in a variety of room styles.
Pragmatism: When you return home, hang your coat, hat, and scarf on 9 hooks, sit on the bench, take off your shoes, and place them on 2 metal grids.
Robust and durable: The strong iron frame and sturdy vintage-style shelf with vintage-style chipboard, practical bench, and practical hooks.
Easy assembly: Thanks to the easy-to-follow instructions, it takes little effort to set up this coat shoe rack for your hallway.

quickview_content.productComments:
Happy with my purchase and put it together successfully on my own. Pleased to see spare screws though I didn't need them. I might take the seat off so the longer coats don't crease. This is a fault with many Hall trees in my price range that they do not allow for full length coats. Hanging from the rail helps.  
There is plenty of shelf space for shoes and underneath.
quickview_content.reviewerLocation: Forest Hall Newcastle Upon Tyne, GB

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Hall Tree 72.5cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
features_array: Overall: 184.5cm H x 72.5cm W x 33cm D

quickview_content.productComments: Perfect size to hold plenty of coats but doesn’t dominate the hallway. Easy to assemble and sturdy once completed. Very happy with my purchase.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Abry Hall Tree 64cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Good quality, sturdy and very pretty!

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Hallway Coat Stand Steel Hall Tree with Shoe Storage
features_array: Overall: 188cm H x 68cm W x 32cm D

quickview_content.productComments: Easy to put together good size, very sturdy

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Ahmet Hall Tree 90cm Wide

quickview_content.productComments:
Its very nice , it’s practical, good size, very easy to assemble and steady 
I loved that every piece is numbered and every nail type is packaged alone with it’s number to ease the process 
My only issue that it’s not white or even of white at all it is closer to beige

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Centreville Hall Tree with Shoe Storage
features_array: : 1 shoe cabinet and 1 wall panel with 6 hooks, 1 shelf and 1 large mirror

quickview_content.productComments: Some screws missing, hard to understand instructions.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Aluesi Hall Tree 122cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Much better quality then I expected for the price. Really sturdy and beautifully constructed.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Tyrese Hall Tree 60cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
features_array: 8 robust hooks to keep your coats, keys, hats, and scarves organized and easy to access
Shoe rack: The bottom metal holds your daily footwear in one place, saving your precious time on searching and pairing

quickview_content.productComments: Love it! Just right for the space. A little more solid that I expected so bonus

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Abrahamson Hall Tree with Bench and Shoe Storage
features_array: Overall: 170cm H x 40cm W x 80cm D

quickview_content.productComments: Love how it looks and very well made. Each piece was lettered so saved time working it out. Also, each fitting was numbered and in separate bags which saved even more time!

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Navara Anyea Hall Tree with Bench

quickview_content.productComments: Really well made and easy to assemble always buy Wayfair first as good value and solid furniture

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Hallway Unit
features_array: Overall: 180cm H x 73cm W x 43cm D

quickview_content.productComments: Very pleased, well made and very easy to put together, I recommend this unit from Wayfair

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Absa Hall Tree 65cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments: It arrived, as usual with Wayfair, very well packed and the build instructions were very easy to follow. The unit was exactly as advertised. We are very pleased with the product.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Johnathon Hall Tree 80cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
features_array: 8 robust to keep your coats, keys, hats, and scarves organized and easy to access
Shoe rack: The bottom wood holds your daily footwear in one place, saving your precious time on searching and pairing

quickview_content.productComments:
Absolutely love it!! Not only organises my coats and shoes but it looks absolutely great and sturdy! 
We bought 2 and disposed them perpendicularly in a corner. Neat!

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Limestone Hall Tree 65.1cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
features_array: Flat-packed for quick and easy home assembly

quickview_content.productComments: Lovely item and easy to assemble. Exactly what we wanted. Quick delivery as always.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Airik Hall Tree 100cm Wide Shoe Storage Bench
features_array: Spacious Coat Rack for Any Hallway
Simple Styling with Weathered Oak Look

quickview_content.productComments: Great once put together but some holes were out of alignment so took longer to put together than expected. Fixing to wall is a must for stability , looks great in our hallway.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Octave Sufy Hall Tree with Bench
features_array: Flat-packed for quick and easy home assembly

quickview_content.productComments: This is a nice unit the only problem is where you screw in the thin coat of white paint etc has come off.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Hall Tree 100cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments:
Extremely easy to assemble.
Looks far more expensive than it costs.
Fits nicely into the hallway, and with the bench, the hooks, the shoe rack, the fabric pockets (ideal for post delivered to pop into for the rest of the house to fetch as they come in), and the mirror - it really is a fully functional hall tree and well worth the purchase - especially if you've not had a hall tree before - you will not be disappointed.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Lafontaine Hall Tree 111cm Wide

quickview_content.productComments: The unit is lovely. Had a bit of trouble getting the right pieces at first but the customer service was quick to send out the replacement parts. Not all pieces had the holes drilled ready to fit in place but managed to put it together without breaking the parts.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Ameila Hall Tree 100cm Wide

quickview_content.productComments: Super easy to build, looks great in my hallway.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Alanas Hall Tree 100cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
features_array: A multifunctional rack for hats, shoes and coats
Versatile hooks and shelf included, large storage capacity
Strong and supportive metal frame for reliable sturdiness

quickview_content.productComments: Love it. Sturdy, smart

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Candee Hall Tree 43cm Wide
features_array: There are 8 hooks on all sides useful for hanging bags/scarfs/hats/coats as well
The sturdy storage shelf is durable, space-saving, and well-organized, taking up minimal space, you can even put it in the corner as scenery

quickview_content.productComments:
Well, once I finally succeeded in putting it together...its great. Sturdy, modern with a small footprint. Plenty of hooks, 3 generous shelves and room to hang coats  on the rail.
BUT I have to say that...assembling it was the mother of ALL nightmares. Lots of frustration  tears. It needs two people for sure! Possibly worth paying the fee to have a professional build it for you.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Cannes Hall Tree 90cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
features_array: Overall: 180cm H x 90cm W x 36cm D

quickview_content.productComments: Went together easily, fitted in the space we had and was the look we wanted for our budget

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Reno Hall Tree 84cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Amazing product, really well made and went together like a dream!

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Coat Rack Shoe Storage Height Adjustable Hall Tree with Bench Kupski
features_array: Height Adjustable: Upper compartment height is adjustable according to your needs
Modern hallway coat rack and shoe storage shelf
Four hanger metal hooks with 5 kg holding capacity
Made of 18 mm thick melamine board

quickview_content.productComments: Great unit, stylish. Easy to put together. Very quick delivery

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Abdul-Quddus Hall Tree 85cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Great item! Looks exactly like in the photos.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Regitze Hall Tree 80cm Wide with Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments: Well pleased, very sturdy.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Severo Hall Tree 85cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
Antavious Hall Tree 90.5cm Wide with Bench and Shoe Storage
Thorbern Hall Tree with Shoe Storage

quickview_content.productComments: The product is nice and we got it for a good price however there were some scuffs and marks which didn't quite fit the "Wayfair quality" we had expected. The instructions had been photocopied so there were corners missing and the shorter screws would not hold the handles and pegs in place which meant a motley job of finding similar sized ones to fit the job. The final piece is nice but only if you are up for a challenge.

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Pal Hall Tree 116cm Wide with Shoe Storage
features_array: Overall: 180cm H x 116cm W x 48cm D

quickview_content.productComments:
Nice enough product but not worth the money charged, even on offer, we paid £404 but I think £200 is the most it is actually worth.  If I had seen it in a showroom there is no way I would have bought it at that price.

Assembly instructions OK but not great (door hinges face the other way to what instructions say)

Delivery was good though

browse_grid_objects.product_name: Adison Hall Tree with Shoe Storage Stylish Entryway Organizer

quickview_content.productComments:
I wanted a different colour, but it was out of stock, so we choose the turquoise combination. I hope it will be more teal, but its still a nice colour. The light moca colour goes very well with out grey oak flooring.
The shoe storage fits more shoes as expected, but men shoes has to place diagonal to the cabinet. Also the door is not soft opening and hits the floor suddenly, so you have to open and close it carefully to not injure yourself.
We didnt put the hooks and a mirror on the wall yet, but cant wait to see it in full. It should be a perfect fit for our little entrace area.

<script async>window.wf_pixel_generic_signifyd = (data) => {
  // if store_id is missing
  if (!data.store_id) {
    return;
  }

  const generateRandomGuid = () => {
    return 'xxxxxxxx-xxxx-4xxx-yxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx'
    .replace(/[xy]/g, function (c) {
        const r = Math.random() * 16 | 0,
            v = c == 'x' ? r : (r & 0x3 | 0x8);
        return v.toString(16);
    });
  }

  /**
   * This function retrieves a cookie if it exists.
   *
   * @param {String} key cookie name being fetched
   *
   * @returns cookie value
   */
  const getCookie = (key) => {
    const cookieEntry = document.cookie.split(';').find(attribute => {
      return attribute.trim().startsWith(key + '=');
    });

    return cookieEntry ? cookieEntry.split('=')[1] : null;
  }

  /**
   * This function saves a cookie with a explicit expiration time. Returns true on success.
   *
   * @param {String} cookieKey              cookie name
   * @param {String} cookieValue            cookie value
   * @param {Number} expirationMilliseconds expiration time in milliseconds
   * @param {Object} attributes             cookie attributes map
   *
   * @returns boolean true if cookie was succesfully saved.
   */
  const setCookie = (cookieKey, cookieValue, expirationMilliseconds, attributes = {}) => {
    // reject calls without key, value, or expiration time
    if (!cookieKey || !expirationMilliseconds) {
      return false
    }

    // convert attributes into cookie attributes
    const cookieAttributes = Object.entries(attributes).reduce((attributesArray, [attributeKey, attributeValue]) => {
      if (attributeValue !== null) {
        attributesArray.push(`${attributeKey}=${attributeValue}`);
      } else {
        // don't insert empty value if there is no value
        attributesArray.push(attributeKey);
      }

      return attributesArray
    }, []).join(';');

    // add expiration milliseconds onto the current milliseconds. Date() handles the carryover logic.
    const expirationDate = new Date();
    expirationDate.setTime(expirationDate.getTime() + expirationMilliseconds);

    document.cookie = `${cookieKey}=${cookieValue};expires=${expirationDate};${cookieAttributes}`;

    return true;
  }

  // ===============================================================================
  // Start of business logic

  // 24 hour timeout before resetting session cookie
  const cookieTimeoutInMilliseconds = 24 * 60 * 60 *  1000;
  // check every 10 seconds if the cookie has been cleared.
  const cookieCheckTime = 10 * 1000;

  // Boolean for checking if signifyd script has been imported
  let scriptTag = document.getElementById('sig-api');

  // set the session cookie if necessary with 24 hour timeout. This will be used by fraud team.
  // reset the cookie if a purchase occured
  let cookieValue = getCookie('FVSID');
  if (!cookieValue || data.purchase) {
    cookieValue = `${data.store_id}-${generateRandomGuid()}`;

    // set new cookie value and set new script attribute value
    setCookie('FVSID', cookieValue, cookieTimeoutInMilliseconds);
    // this will reset the cookie on purchase if the script already exists
    if (!!scriptTag) {
      scriptTag.setAttribute('data-order-session-id', cookieValue);
    }
  }

  // signifyd script has already been imported, return and don't create new script or setInterval
  if (!!scriptTag) {
    return;
  }

  // Import the signifyd script with expected attributes
  scriptTag = document.createElement('script');
  scriptTag.defer = true;
  scriptTag.type = 'text/javascript';
  scriptTag.id = 'sig-api';
  scriptTag.setAttribute('data-order-session-id', cookieValue);
  scriptTag.src = 'https://cdn-scripts.signifyd.com/api/script-tag.js';
  document.head.appendChild(scriptTag);

  // check every ten seconds and set cookie if missing (accounts for 24 hour timeout)
  setInterval(() => {
    const cookieExists = getCookie('FVSID');

    // only set a new cookie if no cookie currently exists
    if (!cookieExists) {
      const newCookieId = `${data.store_id}-${generateRandomGuid()}`;

      // set new cookie value and set new script attribute value
      setCookie('FVSID', newCookieId, cookieTimeoutInMilliseconds);
      scriptTag.setAttribute('data-order-session-id', newCookieId);
    }
  }, cookieCheckTime);
};
